<item>
            <title>[LU-13589] PFL &quot;lfs setstripe -E 1M -S 65536&quot; incorrectly parses stripe_size units </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13589</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Creating a PFL file with &quot;&lt;tt&gt;lfs setstripe -E 1M -S 65536 ...&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; incorrectly transfers the component-end &apos;&lt;tt&gt;M&lt;/tt&gt;&apos; unit to the stripe_size argument, which results in &quot;&lt;tt&gt;65536&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; being parsed as 65GiB.  If the component end is specified as &quot;&lt;tt&gt;-E 1G&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; then the &quot;&lt;tt&gt;-S 65536&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; argument is parsed as 64TiB.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
